Please file this bug report at https://github.com/flutter/flutter-intellij/issues/new.

---

## What happened

--- Started AndroidStudio with an existing project. I've tried recreating the project from scratch using just the lib
directory and pubspec.yaml (plus android/build.gradle, android/app/build.gradle, and  android/app/src/main/AndroidManifest)

Keeps recreating this problem

## Version information

Android Studio `Bumblebee | 2021.1.1 Patch 2` • Flutter plugin `io.flutter 65.1.2` • Dart plugin `211.7808`

Error getting Flutter sdk information.
